  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>2 AP</strong> in Combat to channel raw magical energy for 1 minute, or until you become <strong>Incapacitated</strong>, die, or choose to end it early at any time for free.</p><p>For the duration, your magic is overloaded and you are subjected to the following effects:</p><ul><li>You gain +5 to all Spell Checks you make.</li><li><p>You must immediately make an <strong>Attribute</strong> <strong>Save</strong> (your choice) against your <strong>Save</strong> <strong>DC</strong> upon using this Feature, and again at the start of each of your turns. <br><strong>Failure:</strong> You gain <strong>Exhaustion</strong>. You lose any Exhaustion gained in this way when you complete a <strong>Short</strong> <strong>Rest</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
